title: Woman Superhero
description:
A woman who wields abilities beyond those of ordinary people and is dedicated to protecting the public. Generally depicted as wearing a colorful domino mask and a cape.

The Supervillain is the nemesis of this emoji.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the woman superhero emoji embodies strength and empowerment, depicted with a dynamic pose and a flowing cape that catches the light with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading. Her determined expression and vibrant costume, rendered with realistic lighting, exude confidence and capability. This emoji on Apple devices is perfect for celebrating achievements, inspiring others, or representing a powerful female figure.
